{"type":"message","id":"2a0321fe","parentId":"0530bc67","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:18:37.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Done — I rewrote your core agent markdown files to better match the example folder’s style: shorter sections, denser bullets, more direct phrasing, and less repetition.\n\nUpdated:\n- `AGENTS.md`\n- `SOUL.md`\n- `IDENTITY.md`\n- `USER.md`\n- `TOOLS.md`\n\nWhat stayed intact:\n- medical-only scope\n- Patient Agent / Doctor Agent authority split\n- red-flag and emergency escalation behavior\n- preliminary-not-diagnostic framing\n- tool constraints and relevant capabilities\n- identity/tone as a cautious specialist support agent\n\nIf you want, I can do a second pass and make them even closer to the example files’ voice line-by-line, or keep this as the cleaner doctor-agent-specific version.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_008f5ea62c4373dd0169b3f288bb288191bf88ee23f65beb75\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":19262,"output":162,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20960,"cost":{"input":0.048155,"output":0.00243,"cacheRead":0.000384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05096900000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773400711215}}
